    "description": {
      "value": "<div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Quick to notice details of your environment, you gain the following benefits:</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">Increase your Intelligence or Wisdom by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">If you can see a creature's mouth while it is speaking a language you understand, you can interpret what it's saying by reading its lips.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You have a +5 bonus to your passive Wisdom (<span class=\"help--hover\" onmouseover=\"Renderer.hover.handlePredefinedMouseOver(event, this, 9, {})\" onmousemove=\"Renderer.hover.handlePredefinedMouseMove(event, this)\" onmouseleave=\"Renderer.hover.handlePredefinedMouseLeave(event, this)\" ontouchstart=\"Renderer.hover.handleTouchStart(event, this)\">Perception</span>) and passive Intelligence (<span class=\"help--hover\" onmouseover=\"Renderer.hover.handlePredefinedMouseOver(event, this, 10, {})\" onmousemove=\"Renderer.hover.handlePredefinedMouseMove(event, this)\" onmouseleave=\"Renderer.hover.handlePredefinedMouseLeave(event, this)\" ontouchstart=\"Renderer.hover.handleTouchStart(event, this)\">Investigation</span>) scores.</li></ul></div>\n\t\t</div>",
